headline: Procter & Gamble Builds Health Portfolio And Community Trust With New Moves
summary: Procter & Gamble (NYSE:PG) is acquiring Wonderbelly, a "free from" digestive wellness brand, expanding its health and wellness portfolio. The company is also deploying its Disaster Relief Program in Mississippi after a severe winter storm, supplying essential products and support services. These moves highlight a focus on consumer health trends and community support, outside of routine earnings updates. summary: The Procter & Gamble Company (NYSE:PG) is included among the 12 Best Stocks to Buy for the Long Term.
